      <h1>
        World Wide Web Consortium (W3C)
      </h1><img src="./images/tbl-so.jpeg" style="float:right"
      height="267" width="180" alt="Photo of TBL" title=
      "Tim Berners-Lee" class="withBorder" />
      <blockquote>
        <p>
          &ldquo;To lead the World Wide Web to its full potential
          by developing protocols and guidelines that ensure
          long-term growth for the Web&rdquo;
        </p>
      </blockquote>
      <ul class="incremental">
        <li>Fondato da Tim Berners-Lee nel <a href=
        "http://www.w3.org/Consortium/history.html" title=
        "The history pages of W3C">1994</a>
        </li>
        <li>Definisce <em>Recommendation</em> aperte (<a href=
        "http://www.w3.org/TR/" title=
        "Link to the W3C Publications">Web Standards</a>)
        </li>
        <li>Svolge attivit&agrave; di formazione, sviluppa linee
        guida&hellip;
        </li>
        <li>
          <em>&Egrave; un forum neutrale per creare consenso
          sugli standard web</em>
        </li>
        <li>Gli standard proposti <em>non derivano da posizioni
        dominanti</em> sul mercato
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
